```WARNING ISSUED
${tempVars("executor")} warned ${tempVars("name")}
Reason:
${tempVars("reason")}

If reason is not informative, contact ${member} manually.```

```BOT COMMANDS:

Class: Automatically masks new members. {b!class (PERSON) (COUNT/FOREIGNER/AMBASSADOR) (DEPARTMENT if count)}
Warn: Warns the person in case of a rule violation. {b!warn (PERSON) (REASON)}
Kick: Kicks the person from the server.{b!kick (PERSON) (REASON)}
Ban: Bans the person from the server. {b!ban (PERSON) (REASON)}
Setname: Changes the bot's display name. {b!setname (NAME)}
Say: Bot repeats what is said. {b!say (MESSAGE)}
Delete: Deletes the latest messages. {b!delete (AMOUNT)}
Updatemap: Updates the regional map. {b!updatemap (IMAGE LINK)
Map: Sends a DM with the latest map update. {b!map}```
